HEADWORD: Quadruplication
<hw>Quad`ru*pli*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>quadruplicatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>quadruplication</ets>.]</ety>
<def>The act of making fourfold; a taking four times the simple sum or
amount.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

